{
  "key": 13355,
  "messages": [
    {
      "id": "PastoriaCityEastHouse_Text_TeachMoveForHeartScale",
      "en_US": [
        "Everyone calls me the Pokémon\n",
        "Move Maniac. I prefer Move Tutor.\r",
        "I know every move that Pokémon learn\n",
        "while they’re leveling up, and I can\f",
        "teach Pokémon those moves.\r",
        "I can teach a move to a Pokémon\n",
        "of yours if you’d like.\r",
        "I’ll do it if you’ll trade me\n",
        "a Heart Scale.\r"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "PastoriaCityEastHouse_Text_ThatsAHeartScale",
      "en_US": [
        "Oh! That’s it! That’s an honest-to-\n",
        "goodness Heart Scale!\r",
        "Let me guess, you want me to teach\n",
        "one of your Pokémon a move?\r"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "PastoriaCityEastHouse_Text_ComeBackWithHeartScale",
      "en_US": [
        "If any of your Pokémon needs to learn a\n",
        "move, come back with a Heart Scale."
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "PastoriaCityEastHouse_Text_TutorWhichPokemon",
      "en_US": "Which Pokémon needs tutoring?\r"
    },
    {
      "id": "PastoriaCityEastHouse_Text_TeachWhichMove",
      "en_US": "Which move should I teach?\r"
    },
    {
      "id": "PastoriaCityEastHouse_Text_NoMovesToTeach",
      "en_US": [
        "Sorry...\r",
        "There isn’t any move I can teach\n",
        "that Pokémon."
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "PastoriaCityEastHouse_Text_EggsCantLearnMoves",
      "en_US": [
        "Hunh?\r",
        "Don’t you think it’d be tough for\n",
        "an Egg to learn a move?"
      ]
    },
